                <Header>Elder Care Services</Header>
                <Paragraph>The elder care locator is a public service that provides information on services for older adults and their families. Online chat with an information specialist is also available Monday–Friday, 9 a.m.–8 p.m., eastern time. Phone, 800-677-1116.</Paragraph>
